Miscellaneous Highlights: Frankfurt Arena will host the match between Denmark and England on 20 June 2024 at 18:00. Gates will open at 15:00.
Stadium rules include no bags larger than A4 size, no professional cameras, and no smoking or e-cigarettes.
Public transport is recommended for matchday travel as there will be no stadium parking available.
Fans are advised not to travel to the stadium without a valid match ticket as no tickets will be available for purchase at the stadium.
